text: Ayako Valentina Hamada Villareal (born February 14, 1981 in Mexico City, Mexico) is a Japanese-Mexican professional wrestler currently wrestling on the independent circuit. She is probably best known for wrestling for TNA Wrestling where she won the TNA Knockout Tag Team Championship twice once with Awesome Kong and once with Taylor Wilde. == Other websites == * Ayako Hamada's Official website Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Female professional wrestlers Category:Japanese professional wrestlers Category:Mexican professional wrestlers Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
